creator: XpressSewa
descriptionHtml:
Transfer money on your fingertips
You can now send and receive money in just a few seconds with lower transaction fees and great exchange rates. It is the safest way to transfer money.

Speedy Remit ensures that the remittance process is effortless and fast for users. We provide full transparency, so you have control over your transactions. A thorough verification process is performed to ensure funds are safe and have reached the correct recipient.

Follow these 3 simple steps to transfer money online:

1. Sign up
Enter your email address and phone number to sign up on Speedy Remit.

2. Enter the sending amount.
Enter the amount that has to be sent along with the recipient's details. Later, the transaction fee and the estimated time for delivery can be checked.

3. Almost done
Money will be debited from your account. Money transfer status can also be tracked in real-time in your account.
title: Speedy Remit
